438299959545_7532312566202638856_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7Q5rwxQf8MQQ7kNvgEpYYpt&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-xsp1-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCFEl4g1u2pY6l-a7gHLdwHA_hXGH3pmIXUWicx2Jv5mg&oe=671A2B72"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot4.png", "id": "475352788365462", "uri": "https://scontent-xsp1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974668_475352791698795_6513029807440269328_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=DkFevVdp6vUQ7kNvgF0nftj&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-xsp1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDtaQIezu7jz1IK-NoJKleVvmY7gRSfBlzbsYy2Y63dgw&oe=671A486E"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "TrailerCover.png", "id": "1679571196183084", "uri": "https://scontent-xsp1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982534_1679571199516417_7292601014387023875_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5gseqIkDTmMQ7kNvgEs-liP&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-xsp1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC0WyJ50h6XdjkChp2XrTwVnYMp3l-NdAkySkezDQufzw&oe=671A1D2B"}, "display_name": "XR-Workflow", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Organizations across the world, especially the manufacturing companies, experience difficulty in obtaining expertise for selling & marketing machines digitally, and have to depend on traditional methods of marketing, which result in millions of dollars.\n\nXR-Workflow : VR application enables virtual delivery of contents related to your products for the prospects to help them during the pre-purchase stage, which can work on Meta VR headset devices. It elevates the level of service a user receives without worrying about the impact of geographical boundaries.\n\nXR-Workflow app has various aspects, in several segments of the business such as Remote Auditing, Sales Enablement, Operational Efficacy, Research & Development, On-boarding & Training and  many more.\n\nHighlights of the XR-Workflow App are Product visualization, VR enablement and X-Ray mode simulation.", "short_description": "Redefining immersive product visualization experience."}]}, "